Bidding for Strauss & Co’s first online auction for the year has started, with two pieces by William Kentridge among the artworks going under the hammer. Together with the Kentridge works — Floral Dress, estimated at R15,000-R20,000, and He that Fled his Fate (R50,000-R70,000) — are works by a host of other artists, including David Koloane’s Jo’burg Traffic (R8,000-R12,000). There is also a wide selection of silverware available. You can bid online at www.straussart.co.za.